{"id": 3938, "title": "Ticket #3938: Improve \"condor_status -schedd\" output", "description": "<blockquote>\nI'd like to see improvements in \"condor_status -schedd\" analogous to <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"new\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3937\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3937'); return false;\" title='Improve \"condor_status -submitters\" output'>#3937</a></span>.\n\n<p>In particular, I'd like to see improvements to the reporting of data (may require a new flag; \"-data\"? \"-jobs\"?).\n\n</p><p>For data:\n</p><ul>\n<li>Number of current upload / download processes.\n</li><li>Number of queued upload / download.\n</li><li>Bytes waiting in upload / download queue.\n</li><li>5 minute average KB/s for upload / download\n</li></ul>\n\n<p>For jobs:\n</p><ul>\n<li>Average number of recent job starts.\n</li><li>Average number of shadow starts.\n</li><li>Average memory usage.\n</li></ul>\n\n<p>(probably over the last hour, but should be consistent with whatever we do in <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"new\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3937\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3937'); return false;\" title='Improve \"condor_status -submitters\" output'>#3937</a></span>).</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2016-Sep-20 14:20</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/418b559b6fbd4de8b6da5b4b8761a2454a737cfe\">[49244]</a></span>: Version history for <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5844\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5844'); return false;\" title=\"condor_q -job-ads should support json,xml,new input\">#5844</a></span>, <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5820\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5820'); return false;\" title=\"condor_status should read and write json,xml and new classads\">#5820</a></span> and <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3938\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3938'); return false;\" title='Improve \"condor_status -schedd\" output'>#3938</a></span>  (By John (TJ) Knoeller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2016-Aug-18 10:33</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/7ec151b8d9afecedeadbbc8aa36c7c4ed2b41c66\">[49038]</a></span>: improve condor_status -schedd <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3938\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3938'); return false;\" title='Improve \"condor_status -schedd\" output'>#3938</a></span>. This commit changes: -run now queries schedd running job counts rather than doing the same thing as -claimed -data is a new query that show schedd data transfer stats ===VersionHistory:Pending===  (By John (TJ) Knoeller )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "enhance", "last_change": "2016-Sep-20 14:22", "status": "resolved", "created": "2013-Sep-23 10:03", "fixed_version": "2013-Sep-23 10:03", "broken_version": "v080000", "priority": "4", "subsystem": "Tools", "assigned_to": "johnkn", "derived_from": "#5237", "creator": "bbockelm", "rust": "", "customer_group": "osg", "visibility": "public", "notify": "bbockelm@cse.unl.edu, rynge@isi.edu", "due_date": ""}